## Phase 4: Unified DAG across ALL personas

Apply Tier 2's Phase 4 dependency rules to the unified (deduped) feature
list. Re-sort topologically. Feature rows carry `serves_personas` so
acceptance criteria for each persona can be checked later.

Auth bootstrap priority applies PER PERSONA: if ANY persona needs login and
login is absent, auth lands at position 1.

