## Phase 6: Per-Feature Build Loop

Identical to /auto-feature-build Phase 6 substeps 6a-6f (planning, building,
verify-loop). Read the canonical definition from
`~/.claude/skills/hstack/auto-feature-build/SKILL.md` Phase 6 if needed.

Differences:

- `feature_row.serves_personas` drives which acceptance criteria matter
- The plan file name uses a generic slug (no single persona prefix) since
  the feature may serve multiple personas
- The feature design doc (written in Phase 4) lists ALL served personas
  with their per-persona acceptance criteria

After 6f (verify-loop OK), proceed to 6g **scoped workflow verification for
the primary persona** (the highest-frequency one in `serves_personas`),
then to Phase 6.5 for cross-persona re-verification.

